HEADWORD: expiration-dated
<hw>expiration-dated</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>bearing a date after
which it is no longer valid or salable; -- of a security, option, or
perishable item.</def> <mark>[British]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> expiring, dated.</syn>⟦br⟧
